      "content": "hey, im in rio right now and it’s like crazy hot today. been out at the beach for a few hours and i feel kinda weird. im having a hard time finding the right words when i try to talk and i feel super confused... do u think ive just gotten dehydrated or something? i feel kind of lightheaded too.",
