      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i thought so too. i just feel really out of it. my head is spinning a bit and my face feels kind of tingly or numb on one side but id rather not go to a hospital in this heat if i can help it. i have some leftover coconut water and some sports drinks, should i just drink a bunch of those and sleep it off for an hour?",
