      "content": "okay i'll try to sip the coconut water slowly. i'm just really worried about the numbness on my face... it feels like a weird twitch. but honestly a doctor sounds so intense and i'm pretty sure it's just the sun. you're sure resting and drinking this stuff is the best way to handle it right now? i should be okay if i just stay in the shade for a bit, right?",
